NOTE:::
--If you get a conflict, Git will stop and tell you:
CONFLICT (content): Merge conflict in <file>
--You must fix the conflict manually in that file, then run:

git add <file>
git rebase --continue

--If you want to cancel the rebase:

git rebase --abort
